Description: Ten painted wooden shabti figures of Henutmehyt.
Curator's comments: Published : C. Andrews, Egyptian Mummies, BMP, (1984), p. 61, fig. 76. N. Billing, Nut the Goddess of Life, USE 5 (2002), p. 420, fig. F.1 (drawing).

Published: J. H. Taylor, 'The Burial Assemblage of Henutmehyt: Inventory, Date and Provenance' in W. V. Davies (ed), Studies in Egyptian Antiquities: A Tribute to T. G. H. James (BM Occasional Paper 123, 1999), 59-72.
